name: BRENDA SMITH
text: We came into this resturant Saturday July 1st. The food is typical Pizza Hut in my opinion not bad but not great. I guess what sets this place apart from most was the Customer Service! We had a bit of an issue that day we were just driving …More

text: Hadn't ordered here in a long time.. Glad I did, our pizza was good & delivery service was great.. Thank you Dianne!!

text: Love the crust still, but they skimp on toppings and don't put enough sauce on.

text: We ordered our food & when we came to pick it up, the manager-in-training was indignant & exasperated because we asked for bread sticks. Sorry we inconvenienced you, when we're in town again, we'll go to Blake's Lotaburger!
